#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an4.1"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.1:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.1:0.2"
msgid "1. Bhaṇḍagāmavagga "
msgstr "1. At Bhaṇḍa Village "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an4.1:0.3"
msgid "1. Anubuddhasutta "
msgstr "1. Understood "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p><span class="evam">
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.1, sc1
msgctxt "an4.1:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—"
msgstr "So I have heard. "

#. HTML: </span>
msgctxt "an4.1:1.2"
msgid "ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā vajjīsu viharati bhaṇḍagāme. "
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying in the land of the Vajjis at the village of Bhaṇḍa. "

msgctxt "an4.1:1.3"
msgid "Tatra kho bhagavā bhikkhū āmantesi: "
msgstr "There the Buddha addressed the mendicants, "

msgctxt "an4.1:1.4"
msgid "“bhikkhavo”ti. "
msgstr "“Mendicants!” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.1:1.5"
msgid "“Bhadante”ti te bhikkhū bhagavato paccassosuṃ. "
msgstr "“Venerable sir,” they replied. "

msgctxt "an4.1:1.6"
msgid "Bhagavā etadavoca: "
msgstr "The Buddha said this: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an4.1:2.1"
msgid "“Catunnaṃ, bhikkhave, dhammānaṃ ananubodhā appaṭivedhā evamidaṃ dīghamaddhānaṃ sandhāvitaṃ saṃsaritaṃ mamañceva tumhākañca. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, not understanding and not penetrating four things, both you and I have wandered and transmigrated for such a very long time. "

msgctxt "an4.1:2.2"
msgid "Katamesaṃ catunnaṃ? "
msgstr "What four? "

msgctxt "an4.1:2.3"
msgid "Ariyassa, bhikkhave, sīlassa ananubodhā appaṭivedhā evamidaṃ dīghamaddhānaṃ sandhāvitaṃ saṃsaritaṃ mamañceva tumhākañca. "
msgstr "Noble ethics, "

msgctxt "an4.1:2.4"
msgid "Ariyassa, bhikkhave, samādhissa ananubodhā appaṭivedhā evamidaṃ dīghamaddhānaṃ sandhāvitaṃ saṃsaritaṃ mamañceva tumhākañca. "
msgstr "immersion, "

msgctxt "an4.1:2.5"
msgid "Ariyāya, bhikkhave, paññāya ananubodhā appaṭivedhā evamidaṃ dīghamaddhānaṃ sandhāvitaṃ saṃsaritaṃ mamañceva tumhākañca. "
msgstr "wisdom, "

msgctxt "an4.1:2.6"
msgid "Ariyāya, bhikkhave, vimuttiyā ananubodhā appaṭivedhā evamidaṃ dīghamaddhānaṃ sandhāvitaṃ saṃsaritaṃ mamañceva tumhākañca. "
msgstr "and freedom. "

msgctxt "an4.1:2.7"
msgid "Tayidaṃ, bhikkhave, ariyaṃ sīlaṃ anubuddhaṃ paṭividdhaṃ, ariyo samādhi anubuddho paṭividdho, ariyā paññā anubuddhā paṭividdhā, ariyā vimutti anubuddhā paṭividdhā, ucchinnā bhavataṇhā, khīṇā bhavanetti, natthi dāni punabbhavo”ti. "
msgstr "These noble ethics, immersion, wisdom, and freedom have been understood and comprehended. Craving for continued existence has been cut off; the attachment to continued existence is ended; now there are no more future lives.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an4.1:3.1"
msgid "Idamavoca bhagavā. "
msgstr "That is what the Buddha said. "

msgctxt "an4.1:3.2"
msgid "Idaṃ vatvāna sugato athāparaṃ etadavoca satthā: "
msgstr "Then the Holy One, the Teacher, went on to say: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.2, sc4
msgctxt "an4.1:4.1"
msgid "“Sīlaṃ samādhi paññā ca, "
msgstr "“Ethics, immersion, and wisdom, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.1:4.2"
msgid "vimutti ca anuttarā; "
msgstr "and the supreme freedom: "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.1:4.3"
msgid "Anubuddhā ime dhammā, "
msgstr "these things have been understood "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.1:4.4"
msgid "gotamena yasassinā. "
msgstr "by Gotama the renowned. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "an4.1:5.1"
msgid "Iti buddho abhiññāya, "
msgstr "And so the Buddha, having insight, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.1:5.2"
msgid "dhammamakkhāsi bhikkhunaṃ; "
msgstr "explained this teaching to the mendicants. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.1:5.3"
msgid "Dukkhassantakaro satthā, "
msgstr "The teacher made an end of suffering, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.1:5.4"
msgid "cakkhumā parinibbuto”ti. "
msgstr "seeing clearly, he is extinguished.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.1:5.5"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
